            "title": "Rocket Lab, AST SpaceMobile, Virgin Galactic Shares Are Rising After Hours: What&#39;s Going On?",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-elIZNR kFLUDc\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Space stocks are rising in Thursday’s after-hours session amid an escalation of a public dispute between SpaceX’s <strong>Elon Musk</strong> <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/news/politics/25/06/45800612/trump-says-musk-has-trump-derangement-syndrome-as-battle-over-bill-heats-up-had-a-great-relationship-dont-know-if-we-will-anymore\" target=\"_blank\">and President <strong>Donald Trump</strong></a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>What Happened:</strong> Musk and Trump are throwing jabs on their respective social media platforms spurred by the former’s disapproval of a large tax bill being pushed by Trump. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">In a Truth Social <a href=\"https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/114632206992330264\" target=\"_blank\">post</a> Thursday afternoon, Trump said the easiest way to cut spending is to get rid of Musk’s government subsidies and contracts. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-exeBjx kjPTmb raptive-ad-placement mx-auto overflow-hidden min-h-[250px] min-w-[300px] raptive-ad-wrapper flex flex-col items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"raptive-ben-content w-full flex items-center justify-center\" id=\"\"></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Musk quickly <a href=\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1930718684819112251\" target=\"_blank\">responded</a> with a post on X, indicating that SpaceX would immediately start decommissioning its Dragon spacecraft, which is currently the only option the U.S. has for carrying crew members to the International Space Station. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">NASA press secretary <strong>Bethany Stevens</strong> chimed in on the dispute, noting that NASA will continue to work with Trump to carry out his vision for the future of space. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">“We will continue to work with our industry partners to ensure the President's objectives in space are met,” Stevens <a href=\"https://x.com/NASASpox/status/1930728558558900435?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1930728558558900435%7Ctwgr%5Ee06d105bd2067e7db775e61b4af3ebf6faa7e713%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F06%2F05%2Fmusk-trump-spacex-dragon-nasa.html\" target=\"_blank\">said</a> in an X post.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"nativo-placement-in-content-ap\"></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Space stocks appear to be rallying in response to the news as investors are optimistic the spat could create more opportunities for other space companies. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Rocket Lab Corp</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"RKLB\" style=\"display:inline-block\">RKLB</span>, which has multiple <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/news/contracts/25/05/45434506/rocket-lab-gets-nasa-contract-to-launch-aspera-astrophysics-mission\" target=\"_blank\">contracts</a> with NASA, saw its shares rise 5.22% in Thursday’s after-hours session, while <strong>AST SpaceMobile Inc</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"ASTS\" style=\"display:inline-block\">ASTS</span> shares climbed nearly 3% at last check.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">AST SpaceMobile is one of <strong>Jeff Bezos’</strong> Blue Origin's top customers. The companies signed a deal in November 2024 for the launch of up to 45 satellites. A Scotiabank analyst <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/news/space/25/06/45776611/ast-spacemobile-stock-climbs-after-analyst-flags-potential-investment-from-amazons-jeff-bezos\" target=\"_blank\">speculated this week</a> that the relationship between the two companies could get even stronger in the near future. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-koiXkd gdYKDS\"></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Shares of heavily-shorted <strong>Virgin Galactic Holdings Inc</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"SPCE\" style=\"display:inline-block\">SPCE</span> were also up nearly 15% in after-hours at the time of writing.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">The dispute between Musk and Trump comes about two weeks after Trump <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/general/space/25/05/45532125/l3harris-stock-moves-higher-after-being-named-in-golden-dome-missile-defense-system\" target=\"_blank\">announced</a> the architecture for a $175 billion Golden Dome missile defense system. The system will feature next-generation technologies, including “space-based sensors and interceptors” and “a lot” of American companies will be involved, according to Trump. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">The tax bill, referred to as Trump’s “big, beautiful bill” is expected to include $175 billion for the Golden Dome project.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45805188\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/etfs/specialty-etfs/25/06/45804512/trump-musk-feud-gets-ugly-etfs-exposed-with-tesla-caught-in-the-crossfire\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Trump-Musk Feud Gets Ugly: ETFs Exposed With Tesla Caught In The Crossfire</strong></a></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Photo: courtesy of Rocket Lab.</em></p><!--/$--></div></div>",
            "image": "https://www.benzinga.com/files/images/story/2025/06/05/Rocket-LabF26-Liftoff3-High2.jpeg",
